body:
Hello summoners!

Who and what?  {{summoner:4}} 
My name is Tryden and I am a Mid Lane Main. I am lookin for a srs. team to play ranked or just for fun. 5vs5 and 3vs3 are both possible. I prefer 5v5 :). I also prefer that the team members are also around platin.

About me  {{champion:31}} (< i am cute right?)
I am male and in april i will become 18. I live in Austria. I speak german, english and serbian. I play league since S2. In S2 i was silver and S3 i was gold. In S4 my highest rank was Plat 2 100p. In this season i am Plat 3 (playing ranked rarely becouse soloq is my personal hell --> thats why i search for a team :3)

If you have any questions or even interested on me, please add me in League and in Skype. LoL nick.: Tryden Skype: fixbogi (dont get scared by my this nickname, its old {{summoner:3}} ) 

P.s. I have a good headset and PC/internet so dont worry about that stuff and sorry for the bad english {{summoner:11}}
